  "original_title": "\u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bca\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bcb \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Litro has purchased one lakh metric tons of gas",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Litro Gas Company under the Ministry of Finance has successfully procured 100,000 MT lb of gas, the Prime Minister's Office said in a statement.",
        "The total cost of the gas is estimated at $ 90 million, of which $ 70 million will be provided by the World Bank and the remaining $ 20 million by Litro.",
        "In this case, it has been reported that the said gas will be enough to supply the country for four months, 70% of the gas will be supplied to domestic consumers. Out of this, 5 million 12.5 kg cylinders, 1 million 5 kg cylinders and 1 million 2.5 kg cylinders will be procured and the remaining 30% of the gas will be supplied for commercial use.",
        "It is noteworthy that it has been reported that 33,000 tons of LPG gas purchased by Litro at a cost of $ 20 million will arrive in Sri Lanka in the first week of July."
      ],
